_:N2b3a8765a0c34fc59c37edb775e97a6a <http://schema.org/name> "John Grierson" .
_:N2b3a8765a0c34fc59c37edb775e97a6a <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://schema.org/Person> .
_:N2b3a8765a0c34fc59c37edb775e97a6a <http://schema.org/description> "<p>John Grierson began his nuclear industry career as an apprentice electrician at Chapelcross site, where he later became site director.</p>\n\n<p>Over nearly four decades, John has held a variety of roles, including operations manager and head of defueling projects at Sellafield, deputy site director at Bradwell, and programme director for intermediate level waste.</p>\n\n<p>He served as site director at Hunterston and Chapelcross, and his previous appointment as acting managing director at Dounreay means he has led all of NRS’s Scottish sites.</p>\n\n<p>In 2020, John became nuclear operations director for NRS, where he led the company’s response to the COVID-19 pandemic and the subsequent restart of sites. John is a strong advocate for wellbeing across the business and serves as the executive sponsor for mental health and the men’s health network at NRS Sites.</p>\n" .
